title: Testout - Exchange Server 2007 70-236 - ISO - No Activation
description:
Testout - Exchange Server 2007 70-236 - ISO - No Activation Code. Sorry :-)

1. Install old TestOut Training i.e, 70-294. (it will install by default folder C:Program FilesTESTOUT)
2. Extract Exchange Server 2007 ISO files/folders in a new folder (i.e, c:70-236)
3. Browse the default folder C:Program FilesTESTOUT, then rename 5 folders (Glossary, Outlines, Questions, resources, Sims) to any name (i.e, Glossary2, Outlines2, Questions2, resources2, Sims2) 
4. Copy same named 5 folders from c:70-236 folder to C:Program FilesTESTOUT
5. rename XML file in Outlines folder from ms236cle to ms294cle (i.e, C:Program FilesTESTOUTOutlinesms294cle)
